/ Observables :--

1. A sequence of items that arrive asynchronously over time.
2. HTTP call -- single item.
3. Single iteam -- HTTP response.


// HTTP, Observables and RXJS :--

1. HTTP Get request from service.
2. Receive the observable and cast it in to an array.
3. Subscribe to the obserbavle from components.
4. Assign the array to a local variable.

// RxJS :-- It is a library that enables us towards with Observables in angular applications.

1. Reactive Extensions for javascript.
2. External library to work with Observables.